snippet.textDisplay:
Man, I wished I got my Gran onto this. I saw your video from a year ago and thought that my Gran would have loved it but life gets in the way and since then passed.
I have countless memories of being with her, more so than most grandsons could ask for but I really wished I had got her onto this wholesome little game just so I could visit her island every so often.
